                We are passionate about building innovative, user-friendly, and reliable solutions that make life simpler.
                Our mission is to combine clean design with powerful functionality, creating experiences that leave a lasting impression.
              </p>
              <p>
                With a commitment to quality and attention to detail, we ensure every project reflects our values.
                Whether it’s crafting stunning interfaces, developing seamless applications, or delivering tailored solutions,
                we put our heart into every step.
              </p>

              <div class="values-grid">
                <div class="value">
                  <i class="fa-solid fa-lightbulb"></i>
                  <h4>Innovation</h4>
                  <p>Always improving the experience and reliability of reminders.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="value">
                  <i class="fa-solid fa-shield-heart"></i>
                  <h4>Integrity</h4>
                  <p>Privacy-first design with transparent, predictable behavior.</p>
                </div>
